\id 2CO - Borna New Testamnet 
\h 2 K'orontos 
\toc2 2 K'orontos 
\toc1 2 K'orontos Ashwots Maants 
\toc3 2 K'or. 
\mt3 Wosheetso P'awlos Gitl Wosho 
\mt1 K'orontos Ashuwots Maants 
\imt1 Kindo 
\ip P'awlos K'orontos ashuwotssh b́ guut'ts gitlts wosho b́guut'e K'orontosn teshts Ik'i moowunton teshts ayidek't kic'its gonkewora b́tesh. Ik'i meyitsi ashuwots mangts k'efuwotsi biyats botuziyalor P'awlos mano woshosh eents shuno b́detstsok'oniye b́kitsiri, manan b́wotor een geneúwo bísh shiyewo b́falituwok'oniye b́kitsiri. 
\ip B́ wosh shintsi kayatse P'awlos K'orontositse teshts Ik'i moowunton b́detsts gonkewo kitst Ik'i maamanitse tuuts gac'ewonat t k'efoon eegosh t'engidek't boosh bíaanitsok'oni b́kitsir. Manton deshidek't b́fayman boon naandrone etonat t mano maants b́ jiishtsotse bísh shiyeets gene'úwo boosh b́kitsiri. Manats dabtnuwere Yhuditse fa'a krstiyaniwotsi tep'osh tewudi dowon boimetuwok'o boosh b́gawiyiri. B́ s'uwaatsi k'ot'uwotsatsnowere woshets b́woti jangosh t'intsets s'aamiyetsi jangosha aani b́dek'ir. K'orontositsi Ik'i moowutse ash ik ikuwots botoko ari woshetswotsi woshde't P'awlosi kooti wosheke ett bos'aamifo. 
\iot Jamon mas'aafan b́detstso 
\io1 Shinshintsoni 1:1-11 
\io1 P'awlosnat t K'orontositsi Ik'i mowun 1:12—7:16 
\io1 Yhuditse fa'a krstiyaniwots gizi tep'o 8:1—9:15 
\io1 P'awlos woshets woti alo b́ wottsok'osh aani b́dek'oko 10:1—13:10 
\io1 B́ jamon 13:11-14 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Wosh. 18:1\x* Ik' ettsok'on Iyesus Krstossh wosheets wottso P'awlosnat no eshuu T'imotiyosoke. 
\p K'orontos kitotse fa'a Ik' moonat Akayiyin fa'a Krstiyani wotts ash jamwotssh. 
\p  
\v 2 No nihi Ik'oke, no doonz Iyesus Krstosoknowere s'aatonat jeenon itsh wotowe. 
\s1 P'awlos Ik'osh b́t'intsts údo 
\p  
\v 3 Maarts nihonat kup' jam imet Izar Izewer, no doonz Iyesus Krstos nihi Ik'osh údo wotowe,  
\v 4 Noo Ik'oke nodatsiru kúp'iyon gond bek'otse beyiru jamwotsi kúp'sho no falituwok'o Ik'o noon no gond bek' jamotse kúp'shitwe.  
\v 5 Krstos gond bek'o ayidek'at no kayidek'tsok'on hank'o Krstosn kúp'eyo ayide'er datsituwone.  
\v 6 Noo gondo nobek'or it kúp'eyonat kashon daatsitute, no nokúp'iri itwere itkup'twok'owe. Kup'han b́datsewe no ats bodets gond bek'i naari k'amoon it itned'tsoshe.  
\v 7 Noo gond bek'o it kayok'o mank'o no kúp'ono it kayituwok'o no dantsosh itatsere nodetsts jángo kúp'e. 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt 1 K'or. 15:3\x* T eshuwotso! Isiyi datskayotse no beyor no'ats bodts gond bek'o it danetuwok'o geefone, no'ats bodts gond bek'onuwere kurosh nofalitwoniyere bogo no'ats dihit b́ teshtsotse kashon beyosh nojangtso dab k'ut'dek're b́ teshi.  
\v 9 Mank'o k'iro no'ats angshetsok'owe noosh shiyeyat b́ teshi, jaman no'ats b́ boduwere no amaniruwo k'irts tizitu Ik'ona bako no took angon b́ woterawok'o nibn no dek'ishe.  
\v 10 Mansha bí noon hank'o een k'irosh betsit t'úp'er tawatse kashire, kashitwe, dabnwere b́ kashitwok'o bíne nojágiti.  
\v 11 It noosh Ik' k'onon it tep'o geyituwe, ayi ashuwots Ik' k'onatse tuutson noosh imets Ik' s'aatosh aywots udo t'intsitune. 
\s1 P'awlos finosh bí ettso b́wonitsok'o 
\p  
\v 12 No it'et keewo haniye, hanwere ar b́ wotok'o no nibo gawitwe, k'osh ashuwotsnat bítsnooru itnton nobeets beyo Ik'oke nodek'ts S'ayinonat kááwatse tuutsone, han b́ wotuwere Ik' s'aatone b́ teshi bako ash dani telefonaliye.  
\v 13 Nababar t'iwintso it falit keewoniyere okoon k'osho eegoru guud'atsone,  
\v 14 no jangosh k'atso it dantsok'o mank'o s'eenon it danetwok'o amanitwe, manshowere doonzo Iyesus b́ weet aawor no itn noit'etuwok'o itwere noon it'etuute. 
\p  
\v 15 Keewann arik twottsosh gitoto it t'ak'ametuwok'owa etaat shin shino iti s'ilosh geeyatniye tteshi,  
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Wosh. 19:21\x* Itn s'ilosh tietwere Mk'odoniy datso maants it weeron t beshoronat bíyokere aanar twore b́ teshi, hank'onowere Yhud datso maantsan t sha'or taan it tep'etuwk'o gawatniye t teshi.  
\v 17 Hanowere t gawor t k'aliru danaw hake baka etirwok'o arefta itsha? Han t gawirwo iknon «ee, etonat iya'a» etaat ash gawirwok'o hake baka eton t k'altsok'o arefta itsha?  
\v 18 Ik'o amanek b́ wottsotse no nokeewirwo, «ee wee iya'a» etiru hake baka eton keeweyiru aap'ok'oyiyaliye.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Wosh. 18:5\x* Taanat Silasn T'imotiyosu itsh nonabtso Ik' na'o Iyesus K'rstosi «ee wee iya'a» etonaliye b́teshi, ernmó ee eto bín wotere.  
\v 20 Ik'o noosh b́ jangits jamo, «ee» etiruwo Krstosne, mansh Ik' mangosh Krstosn «Amen» no etiri.  
\v 21 Noo itnton Krstosats no kúp'ituwok'o woshtso Ik'oniye, noon galdek' futtso bíne,  
\v 22 Bík nowotok'o kitsit mahatabon no'ats gedtsona shino maants noosh b́ imet gaalosh no níbots S'ayin shayiro agitok'o woshdek't imtso bíne. 
\p  
\v 23 Taa K'orontos maants aanat woo t k'azitsi jango itn tshiyanirawok'o itsh maac'o keewatniye, hansh Ik'o gawosh s'eegetwe,  
\v 24 It it imnetiyon kúp' it wottsotse it itgeneúitwok'o itnton finituwone boko it imnetiyon iti azazeratsone. 
\b  
\c 2  
\p  
\v 1 Eshe iti tshiyanirawok'o gawat iti s'iilo it maants ando aanar twarawok'o k'ut'dek'niye tteshi.  
\v 2 Dab iti tshiyaaniyalor ityere t shiyanitswotsiyere oko taan geneeúshituwo kone?  
\v 3 Mank'o itsh t guut'uwere itok twoor taan geneúsho boon geyit ashuwots taan boshiyanirawok'o geeyatniye, t geneúwo it únets geneúwo b́wottsok'o amanirwe.  
\v 4 Shiyani eenonat nibi kic'on, ay aac'uwonowere wotdek'at itsh tguut' ayidek'at iti tshuntsok'o itdanetwok'owa etni bako iti shiyaaniyosha etaatniyaliye. 
\s1 Dadetsosh orowa etetwok'o b́ iztsok'o 
\p  
\v 5 Ash shiyanitso konwor fa'e wotiyal b́shiyaniyi taan b́woterawo b́ naando k'ees'iyo wot k'aya bako k'osh weeron ititse ayuwotsnoor shiyaanire.  
\v 6 Han naari ashosh ititse ayuwots bíats boangshts fayo bísh bodfe.  
\v 7 Mansha ashaan weeralon shiyaanotse b́kindrawok'o dab maniyere bísh orowa err bín it kup'iyo itsh geyife.  
\v 8 Mank'owere bín it shuntsok'o aaniyi arikon it kiitsituwok'owo iti k'onirwe.  
\v 9 Wosh ekeewnowere itsh tguut' fadeyar jam keewon aletswotsi it woto danoosha etaatniye.  
\v 10 It bísh oorowe it eteet ashosh taawere oorowe etetuwe, bísh oorowe ti eteet naando b́beyalor taa Krstos shinatse oorowe tietet itsha erniye.  
\v 11 Man t k'alirwere shed'ani gond fino nodantsotse shed'ano noon b́ darirawk'owa etaatniye. 
\s1 T'iro'ad datsatse P'awlos b́kic'tsok'o 
\p  
\v 12 Maniyere hakon Krstos doo shishiyo daniyosh T'iro'ad maants ti amor doonzo fini fengsho taash k'eshree,  
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:12-13 \xt Wosh. 20:1\x* Ernmó t eshúwi Titoyi daatso t k'aztsotse t shayiro kash de'atse, mansh manoki krstiyaniwotsi jamiyat Mek'odoniyo maants ti ami. 
\p  
\v 14 Ernmó jam aawo Krstos da'oon noon jishirwonat sheeng sháák' detsts shituwok'o Krstossh no detsts dano jam beyok nobetsitwok'o woshtso Izar Izewersh údo wotowe!  
\v 15 No kashitwotssh wotowa t'afitwotssh wotowa Krstosn Ik'osh sheeng sháák'o detsts it'anok'o noone.  
\v 16 Ikosh k'iro maants jishit k'iri sháák' noone, k'oshosh kasho maants jishit kashi sháák' noone, beré finansh bodts wotituwo kone?  
\v 17 Noo Ik' aap'tso jaak k'ac' kemiru ayuwotsk'o noonaliye, ernmó Ik'oke wosheets kááw woshetswotsk'o wotar Krstosn Ik' shinatse keewituwone. 
\c 3  
\s1 Handr taari gútsuwots 
\p  
\v 1 Ando aani notooko údo tuuwwonoowa? Himo ik ikuwots bok'aliruwok'o itsh wee itoke noon tep'osh guut'etso noosh geyiyifek'úna?  
\v 2 Ash jamo b́ dantswotsnat b́ nababirwotsn nonibots guut'ts dabdabewwots itne.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt Kesh. 24:12; Erm. 31:33; Hzk'. 11:19; 36:26\x* It no finon daatsets Krstos dabdabewotsi it wottsok'o daneke, woshanuwere b́ guut'e beyat beyiru Ik' shayirona bako k'elemiyonaliye, manuwere ash nibatsa bako gashets shúts tabtabats gut'ekaliye. 
\p  
\v 4 Hanowere no etir Krstos weeron Ik'atse nodetsts imnetiyoshe.  
\v 5 Ik keewonwor nowooke b́wottsok'o gawosh flratsone, manwere eegoshe nonotokon bodknoonaliye, ernmó noon bodtswotsi woshtso Ik'oniye.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Erm. 31:31\x* Handr taarosh finirwotsi nowotitwok'o noon falitso bíne, hanuwere fidelon guut'ets nemon b́woteraniyere S'ayin shayiri tep'one, fidelon guut'ets nemo ud'itkee, S'ayin shayironmó kash imetke. 
\p  
\v 7 Nemo fideliyon gashdek't guut'e shúts tabtabatse b́ teshi, nemo imeyori shááno k'aawe'efe bíamiri wotiyaloru Israe'el ashuwots Muse shiitso t'iwints de s'iilo falatsno boteshi, eshe k'ir dowet nemo hank'o mangon b́ be'eyal  
\v 8 bére, S'ayin Shayiri weeron daatset fino bog mango deetsalkeya?  
\v 9 Ashuwotsats morr doots fino hank'o mango b́ detsiyakon ashuwots bín kááw bowotit fino aawuk'oneya bog mango b́ t'ut'eti?  
\v 10 Ilts mango ayidek't bog b́wottsatse tuutson beshts mango eegoru b́ berawok'o tawetwe.  
\v 11 Ili t'afitwonworu hank'o mango b́ detsiyakon, dúre dúrosh kúp'ar beet keewonmó aawuk'oneya bog mango b t'ut'eti! 
\p  
\v 12 Hank'o jangetso nodetstsosh ááwu shúk'on keewitwone.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Kesh. 34:33\x* Muse múk'efere amiru b́ shiits golo b́ t'affetsosh Israe'el ashuwots bo be'awok'o b́ shiitso b́ ipefoni b́ teshi, nooyere Musek'o noonaliye.  
\v 14 Bo nibo arikon dúnguwtsere, andish b́ borfetso nat taari mas'aafo bo nababor bonibo manoori ipetsmann ipetsok'one b́fa'oni. Ipman ipalon b́wotit Krstos s'uzn b́ wottsotsne.  
\v 15 Hambetsish b́ borfetsosh nemi mas'fo nababeyi taawo bonibo ipeyirumann ipeke.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt Kesh. 34:34\x* Ernmó asho doonzo maants bíaanor «Ipeyiruman k'ayb́tuwiti.»  
\v 17 Doonzo shayire, doonzo shiyiri beyokonowere s'ayin kesho fa'ee.  
\v 18 Noo noúnets iperaw shiits wotar doonzo mango mestawtotse bek'eyirwok'o bek'irwone, Shayir wottso doonzo aro aroosh mangoniyere mango maants wonetuwone. 
\c 4  
\s1 Arik wosheets fino 
\p  
\v 1 Ik'o b́ mhretwon bísh finet finan noosh b́imtsotse maac'o k'ut'r shuuts aaneratsone.  
\v 2 Aashtsonat jitsik wotts keewo juuk'rerone, nemi gondon fineratsone, Ik'i aap'ono kooton woniratsone, dab iki ariko sháánatse nokitsiri, notook jangoshmo ash jami nibots Ik'i shinatse ariko keewitwone.  
\v 3 No danits doo shishi aap'o dab ááshka wotiyal bíáásh t'afitwotsshee.  
\v 4 Datsani keewiru shed'ano amaneraw ashuwots níbo deekk'rere, mannowere Ik'i aron be'eetso Krstos b́mangi dooshishiyon boosh b́sháánits shááno bobea'awok'o b́woshi.  
\v 5 Noo nodaniyirwo Iyesus Krstos doonz b́wotonat noowere notookon Iyesus jangosh it guuts nowottsok'oni bako notooko nabratsone.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 4:6 \xt Aze. 1:3\x* «Shááno t'aluwotse shááne!» ett keewts Ik'o Krstos aron goliruwo Ik'i mango dani shááno noosh b́ imetwok'o b́ shááno nonibots b́ sháánetwok'o woshre. 
\p  
\v 7 Ernmó jamoniyere bogts angaan Ik'oka bako nok b́woterawotse mangts keewan shali k'ac'ok'o wotdek'at detsdek'rone.  
\v 8 B́ kaat kaaton gond bek'o noats bodiruwe, ernmó da'eratsone, ayoto daandirwonee, ernmó maac'o k'ut'ratsone.  
\v 9 Giishefoone, ernmó noon shuntswotsi t'ud' danaknone, togeere dihfoone erenmó k'irraknoone,  
\v 10 Iyesus kasho no atsotse b́be'etuwok'o Iyesus ats bodts k'iro noatsatsowere jam aawo kurdek'aatniye nogúúriri.  
\v 11 Iyesus kasho noats k'irituwanitse b́be'etuwok'o no kashetswots Iyesus jangosh jam aawo beshat noimeyiri.  
\v 12 Mansh k'iro noyitse, kasho ityitse b́ finiri. 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 4:13 \xt Dub. 116:10\x* Wotowa eré «Taa amanere, manshe tkeewiri» ett guut'etsok'on, noowere imneti ikman shayiro nodetstsotsene no amaniri, manshowerowe keewirwone.  
\v 14 Doonzo Iyesusi k'irotse tiztso Izar Izewer nonowere Iyesusnton b́ tizituwok'onat itntonwere noon b́ shinats b́ t'intsituwok'o danfone.  
\v 15 Jaman it t'k'imiyosh wotts s'aato s'eent b́ ooyefetsosh ay ashuwotssh b́ bodtsi taawon Ik' mangosh wotit údo bí ayituwok'owe. 
\s1 Imnetiyon beyo 
\p  
\v 16 Mansh no maac'o k'ut'ratsone, úratsi noaro b́ t'afiyaloru gitsitsi no atso aawu aawon handr wotituwe  
\v 17 Keet wotts gond bek' andish nodek'irwan s'uu deshaw ayidek't een wotts dúre dúri mango noosh daatsituwe.  
\v 18 Noo nokotirwo be'eraw keewoni bako be'eyirwoniyaliye, be'eyirwo andkee, be'erawonmó dúre dúrikoniye. 
\b  
\c 5  
\p  
\v 1 And gofok'o wotts datsatsi nomeetso b́gahor ash kishon b́ woterawo Ik'on ageets dúre dúri beyoko darotse nodetstsok'o danfone.  
\v 2 Andi beshit gofanitse nobeyor kashe no k'ushiri.  
\v 3 Mansh no meets datsatsan b́k'alewor araats wotaarr datseratsone.  
\v 4 Arikon k'iritwo kashots b́k'ot'etwok'o tahdek'osha bako noatse giinbazeyo no shunaawotse noo daritsi atso han abaats dabde'er tahdek'o geefone, mansh datsatsi dunkaniyotse fa'uwots noo noats b́mangre kasho nok'as'iri.  
\v 5 Keewansh noon k'anitso Ik'oniye, maniyere bog keewo noosh b́ imetu jamosh agito b́ wotish b́ shayiro noosh imtso bíne. 
\p  
\v 6 Datsatse no atson no befetsosh doonzo'atse no woktsok'o no danaloru jam aawo bín amanetuwone.  
\v 7 No nobeyir amanona bako keewwotsi bek'onaliye.  
\v 8 No beewok wotts meetsanitsere k'aleyar doonzonton wotoshe no tewniri, mansh amanon beetuwone.  
\v 9 No meetsanton nowotiyal wee bíyatse no k'aleyal no k'os'ó doonzo geneúshe.  
\v 10 Datsatsi beyon nok'altso gond wotowa doo keewosh ik iko b́ finok'o b́ k'auntso dek'osh noúnets Krstos angshi jori shinats t'ino noosh geyife. 
\p  
\v 11 Doonzo shato eeg b́wottsok'o no dantsosh, ashuwotssh sheenga err bodek'etwok'o woshitwone, no eeg nowotok'o Ik'o danfee, itwere it nibotse eeg nowotok'o it danetuwok'o jangirwe.  
\v 12 Nibotse beyiruwon b́ woterawo be'eyiruwon it'iruwotssh aaniyo it falituwok'o noon it it'etuwok'o itsh gowo imetuwone bako aani no itsh notooko úderatsone.  
\v 13 Geetsuwotsi no wotiyalowere Ik'osha etaatniye nogeyi, nibetsuwotsi woterone wotiyalowere itsha etaatniye nibetsuwotsi nowoti.  
\v 14 Manjangosh Krstos shuno noon detsetwe. Iko jametsosh b́k'irre jametsotswotswere bok'iro dandek'roone.  
\v 15 Kashon fa'a jamwots boosh k'irtsonat k'irotse tuutsosh bobeetuwok'owa bako haniyak botookosha err boberawok'o Krstos jametswotsshowere k'irre. 
\p  
\v 16 Haniyere okoon noo asho konnor meetsi s'iil s'iilon s'iilatsone, haniyere shin Krstosnor nos'iil ash jamikok'o meetsi s'iil s'iilona wotiyal shinomaants han k'alratsone.  
\v 17 Mansh eshe asho konuwor wotowa Krstos jiro b́wotiyal handr azeeke, nattso beshwtseree, jamonu handr wotwtsere.  
\v 18 Jamhan b́wotuwere noon b́ tookonton Krstosn manitsonat maniyi fino noosh imts Ik'one.  
\v 19 Hanuwere Ik'o Krstosn datsatsi ashjamo b́tookonton maniree etee, bo naandonowere boats taawratse, nooshowere asho doonzonton nomaniyish bí aap'o noosh imre. 
\p  
\v 20 Ik'o ashuwotsi noweeron b́ s'egetwotse Krstos shegro wotat wosherone, mansh «Ik'onton manewere!» err Krstos shútson itn k'onitwone  
\v 21 Noo Krstosn Ik' kááw fino kayituwotsi nowotitwok'o Ik'o morr deshawo Krstosi no morrosh wosho b́wotitwok'o b́ k'ali. 
\c 6  
\p  
\v 1 Ik'onton tohaat finirwotsi nowottsotse itdek'ts s'aato datsmec'ron oorik'r k'ayere etaat itn k'oniruwe.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 6:2 \xt Isa. 49:8\x* Ik'o, 
\q1 «Taash wotts aawots nkeewo k'ebre! 
\q2 Kashiyi aawotsowere neen tep'ree!» bí etirwotse 
\m «Eshe hambe! wotts aawo andee, kashi aawonwere andee.» 
\p  
\v 3 No fino k'efeerawok'o ik keewon konshor t'ugo woteratsone.  
\v 4 Maniyere gond bek'ona, ono bek'ono, k'ic'onowere k'amefetsr Ik'osh finirwotskok'o notooko jam weeron t'intsituwone.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 6:5 \xt Wosh. 16:23\x* Ik'osh fintsuwotsi nowoto nokitsitwere jot'ewon, tipewon, noats tuuzeyiru dimbiron, finon maawon, tokr t'ut'onat s'oomiyonee,  
\v 6 Mank'owere s'ayinon, danon, k'amoon, doowoton, S'ayin shayiron jisheewonat bíats daro bítse aalts shunon,  
\v 7 ari aap'onat Ik' angone. Bín da'osh wotowa noatse k'arbazosh kes'i kac' wotts kááw fino no k'anonat giri kishon deshdek'etwone.  
\v 8 Mangosh wee ketosh, k'orewosh wee údewosh k'an dek'k noone, aretswotsi nowotefere, dirshtswotsi eteyi.  
\v 9 Danetswotsi wotefetsat danerawwotskok'o nowoti, k'irrne etefere hamb kashetswotsi wotat nodatseyri, no jot'eyaloru úd'eratsone,  
\v 10 Shiyano noats b́ bodaloru jam aawo geneúituwone, tuguretswotsi wotefetsat ayuwotsi gaaletso nowoshiri, eegoru deshawwots wotefetsat, jam keewo detsfone. 
\p  
\v 11 It K'orotosn beyiru ashuwotso! hamb, itsh kish dek'at keewurone, no nibonowere gawintsdek'at itsh k'eshrone.  
\v 12 Itna itshuno noosh baziyi bako no itsh bayatsone.  
\v 13 Niho b́nana'úwotssh b́keewfok'o tkeewre, noo nonibo gawunon k'eshde'er nogitsotse shisheyirwo itsh kish nokitstsok'o itwere mank'o noosh k'aluwere. 
\s1 Amaneraw ashuwotsnton ikwotk'azo 
\p  
\v 14 Woteraw finon, amaneraw ashuwotsnton ikn s'andek'ayere, kááwonat morron awuk'o k'alrniya ikwoto bofaliti? Sháánonat t'aluwon towaar beyo aawk'oneya bofaliti?  
\v 15 Krstosnat Diyablosn aawuk'oneya ik woto bofaliti? Amantsonat amanerawonmó aawuk'oneya kod'ewo bofaliti?  
\v 16 \x - \xo 6:16 \xt Lew. 26:12; Hzk'. 37:27; 1 K'or. 3:16; 6:19\x* Ik'i maa S'ayino woteraw dozets ik'uwotsnton eeg ikwote b́detsi? Ik'onwere, 
\q1 «T beyokonowere tiashuwots taalots woshituwe, 
\q2 Bontonwere beetwe, 
\q1 Taa boosh boko Izar Izeweri wotituwe, 
\q2 Bowere ti ashuwotsi wotitúne» 
\m ett b́ keewtsok'on no beyat beyiru Ik'osh S'ayin Ik' maa noone.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 6:17 \xt Isa. 52:11\x* Manats dabt doonzo hank'o etre, 
\q1 «Bo dagotse galeyar keere, 
\q2 Kim wotts keewo t'awik'ayere, 
\q2 Taawere iti dek'etuwe, 
\q1  
\v 18 \x - \xo 6:18 \xt 2 Sam. 7:14; 1 Zen. 17:13; Isa. 43:6; Erm. 31:9\x* Taawere itnihi wotituwe, 
\q2 Itwere t nungush nana'úwotsnat mááts nanaúwotsi wotitute, 
\q2 Etre jam faltso Izar Izeweri.» 
\c 7  
\p  
\v 1 Tmashotso! jam keewo jangit noosh imetsotse atsonat shayiron kimshit kon naari keewatse notooko s'ayitsuwone, Ik' shatoon S'ayin nowoto s'een b́ wotituwok'o woshwone. 
\s1 P'awlos gene'o 
\p  
\v 2 It nibon noon de'ere, no konnoru daderatsone, konatsor gondo fineratsone, dirshon konatsno ik jago geeratsone.  
\v 3 Hano t etir itats angshoshaliye. Haniye shini itsh tkeewtsok'o it no nibots itne, eshe kashon wotowa k'iron jam aawo itatse k'aleratsone.  
\v 4 Itatse tdetsts imnetiyo eene, itatse tdetsts it'o eene, kup'wtsere, nokic' jamon ayide geneúituwe. 
\p  
\v 5 Mek'edoniyots nobodiyakon ay kaaton gondbek'a no atsats bodi bako kash dek'o iknotonor daatsratsone, úratse fayo gitsotsnowere shate nodetsi.  
\v 6 Ernmó juweetswotsi kup'shit Ik'o Izar Izewer Tito b́woon noon kup'shre.  
\v 7 Nokup'uwere b́ waats mec'rosh b́woterawo it bín it kup'shtso noshishtsotsne, t jangosh it detsts mirac'o, shiyanonat tjangosh it kic'irwok'o noosh b́keewre iki tgeneúwi. 
\p  
\v 8 Haniyere shin itsh t guut'ts wosho itn shiyaanik b́wotiyalor dab woshman tguut'tsotse goyineraatse, goyinere wotiyalowere tgoyin twoshon múk'na'a gizewosh itn tshiyanitsotsne.  
\v 9 Andmó gene'owere, tgene'útsonuwere eegoshe itn tshiyanitsosh b́woterawon it shiyantsatse tuutson naandrone etaat itwonetsotsne, eshe it shiyano Ik'o ettsok'o b́wottsotse no itn eegor daderatsone etee.  
\v 10 Ik'o ettsok'on wotts shiyano woro maants jishituwo naandre eton daatset wonewo b́daatsitwotse goyino dooratse, datsatsi shiyanonmó k'ire b́doweti.  
\v 11 It shiyaanan Ik' ettsok'on b́wottsok'owo awuk'o kup'de fino, awuk'o wotts aniyidek'o, awuk'o kááron fayo, awuk'o shato, awuk'o mirac'o, awuk'o okooro, awuk'o sezonowere b́dootsok'owo nibnde'er t'iwintsde s'iilere. Ando it jam keewon s'ayin it wottsok'o gawon gawirute. 
\p  
\v 12 Itsh t guut'alor taa itsh tguut' no jangosh itdetsts kup'ar fino Ik'o shinatse itsh shaanr b́daneetwok'owa etaatni bako morro bín dadets ashosha etaatniyaliye.  
\v 13 Jamanatse tuutson noo kup'erone, no nokup'tsoniyere bogo ando Tito b́daatsts geneúwon iki ayidek'at geneeúweroone, manu eegishe b́shayirosh kashdek'o itdatsitsoshe.  
\v 14 It atse t detsts it'onowere Titosh keewre b́teshi, itwere taan jitsiratste, jam aawo itsh arikeewono itsh keewufoone b́teshi, hanuwere it jango Titosh nokeewtso itn it'o arbwotoon be'ere.  
\v 15 It únetswor azazeyirwotsi itwottsotsnat shatoonat k'ewon bín itdek'tsok'owo Tito b́gawor itsh b́detsts shuno ayidek't eeno wotere.  
\v 16 Taawere jam weeron itn it'o tfaltsotse iki bogshdek' geneúwere. 
\c 8  
\s1 Krstiyaniyots tewdo 
\p  
\v 1 T eshuwotso! Ik'o Mek'odonin fa'a Ik' maa moowwotssh bí imts s'aato itsh daniyo shunfone.  
\v 2 Bowere ay gond bek'on faderne, b́woteferoru bogen'úo ayidek't eene, ayidek't tugurtswotsi bo wotiyaloru dab een teudo woshrne.  
\v 3 Bo faltsok'onat bofaltsoniyere bogo bo shunon bo imtsok'o taa boosh gawitwe,  
\v 4 \x - \xo 8:1-4 \xt Rom 15:26\x* Yhud datsatse beyiru Kirstiyaniwots ash tep'i gowo boosh baziyerawok'o kup'idek't noon bok'oni.  
\v 5 Bowere bo k'oltso no nokotirwoniyere boge, shin shin botoko doonzosh boimi, manats dabtnu Ik' shunok'on botoko noosh imrne.  
\v 6 Finan shin shinon fintso Titoyi b́ wottsotse andoor bo teudi finan s'uwaats de'am b́ betsitwok'o bín k'onitwe  
\v 7 It imnetiyon, noon keew keewon, danon, kup'on, nooke dan itdek'ts shunon jam keewono bogfte, tewd dooyi finannowere it bogetwok'o wotowe. 
\p  
\v 8 Eshe, tietir azazonaliye, ernmó k'oshuwots imon kup' woto it kup' wotonton no nohir it shuno ar b́ woto shu'ar s'iilosha etaatniye.  
\v 9 It no doonz Iyesus Krstos s'aato danfte bí eegoru dab gaaletsk b́ wotiyaloru bí tugurets wotat it galetswotsi it wotituwok'o itsha ett tugretsk b́ woti. 
\p  
\v 10 Han jagosh itsh sheeng araat be'ets izo itsh imetwe, beshts dúron im mec'r b́ woterawo han k'alosh shini geetswots itne b́ teshi.  
\v 11 Eshe imosh it detsts shúno finats jitsit s'uwo maants b́ bodetwok'o it faltsok'on it gawts man and k'aluwere.  
\v 12 Imosh sheeng shun detstso b́ beyal ashman tewdi doon b́ detstso b́ imala boko bíangalon b́ímíshaliye. 
\p  
\v 13 Hanowere ti etir it únets taalo it wotitwok'owa bako it imon it kic'efere k'oshwots bín kash bodek'isha etaatniyaliye  
\v 14 It it kic'or bogizo it kic'ats b́ jinetwok'o and it gizo bok'ic'ats jinee, hank'on it dagotse manuts woto beetwe.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 8:15 \xt Kesh. 16:18\x* Hanwere, «Ayi ko'itswotssh oreratse, múk' ko'itswotsshowere shapratse» ett guut'etsok'one. 
\s1 Titonat b́tohuwotsn 
\p  
\v 16 Taa itsh t shiyanirwok'o Titowere itsh b́ nibon b́ shiyanituwok'o woshts Ik'o údewe.  
\v 17 Tito it maants b́weet b́ took shunon tuut gene'ona bako no nok'onts mec'roshaliye.  
\v 18 Doo shishiy nabon Ik'maa jamooke údetso eshúwo bínton woshitwone.  
\v 19 Haniyere dambon eshuwan no sheeng finan doonzo mangosh nofinorat finosh nodetsts sheeng shuno nokitsor noonton amt nofiinman b́ tep'etwok'o Ik'i moowwots n marat'etsoniye. 
\p  
\v 20 Tewdi doon imets gizan nok'eezor noshútso b́ t'afrawok'o no atso kordek'etwone.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 8:21 \xt Ari. 3:4\x* Noo nogeyiru keewo doonzo shinatse s'uz b́woterawo ashuwots shinatse kááw wotts keewo k'ale. 
\p  
\v 22 Ayoto ay weeron fadere kup'at fintso wotat daatsetso no'eshuwi Titowi bonton woshitwone, bí itatse b́detsts imnetiyo een b́wottsotse and finann iti tep'osh b́detsts kup'at fino awurtsooniyere boge.  
\v 23 Tito jango dano b́geyitka wotiyal itn tep'osh taanton finirwo, fini weeron ttohe, bínton tohaat weyiru k'oshwots jango b́wotiyalowere bo Ik'i moowwotsatse naashuwots, Krstos mangosh need'tswotsiye.  
\v 24 Mansh it shúno boosh kitswere, hank'on it shunonat itatse nodetsts it'o k'awtsalko b́ woterawok'o Ik'i maa jamwotssh kitsitute. 
\c 9  
\s1 Krstiyaniwotssh kisheets gizo 
\p  
\v 1 Yhuditse fa'a krstiyaniwotssh kisheet gizi jango itsh guut'o taan geyiratse,  
\v 2 «Akayiy dats ashuwots natstsoon tuut tep'osh k'andek'kne» etaat mek'edoniitsi ashuwotsoke it jangosh ti ít'ir it kup'ar it finitwok'o t dantsoshe, it kup'at itfiintsonwere k'oshwotsnoor tuuzere.  
\v 3 Keewanatse itatse no detsts it'o dats mec'ro wotar b́oorerawok'o eeshwanotsi woshiirwe, itwere ari taa haniyere shin ti ettsok'o k'ande'er korere.  
\v 4 Mek'edoni dats ashuwots taanton itok waarr itk'ande'aawo bodatsiyal itats noit'tsatse tuutson jiitsitwone, itmó ayde'erniye itjiitsiti.  
\v 5 Mansha imetuwone it etts tewud doon it imiruwo it k'aniyitwok'o itsh bogawitwok'owa etaat eshwaanots taayere shino itok boweetwok'o wosho b́ geyiko b́wottsok'o daatsre, mank'oon taa twoor tewudi dowon it imetuwo k'anke b́wotiti, itwere it imet angnon b́woterawo shunon b́wottsok'owoniye b́kitsiti. 
\p  
\v 6 «Múk'shde shooketwo muk'e b́kakuwiti, ay shooktso aye b́ ko'iyiti» ett keewetso gawde'ere.  
\v 7 Eshe Ik'o b́shunfo geneúwon imet asho b́wottsotse asho ik ikon b́nibotse imosh b́geetso shunr ima bako shiyaanefetsr wee b́maac'otse aalo imk'aye.  
\v 8 Jam aawo jamkeewon it tooko falr shengfiinats jinosh itfalitwok'o ayide b́ deero itsh imo falfe.  
\v 9 «Hanwere t'owwotssh tewdi dowon imre, 
\q2 B́ kááw finonwere dúre dúrosh beetuwe» 
\m et t guut'etsok'one. 
\p  
\v 10 Shooko shooktsosh, moowosh misho imirwo Izar Izewer it shooket shooko ayde'er imetwe, it kááwi shuwonowere itsh ayituwe.  
\v 11 It tewdi doo noweeron boosh b́bodiru ash jamwots Ik'o bo úditwok'o jam aawo it imetwok'o Ik'o jam keewon iti deritwe.  
\v 12 It kaliru tewdi finan krstiyaniyots kic'otse kishoniyere bogo ashuwots Ik'osh ay udo bot'intsitwok'o woshitwe.  
\v 13 It tewdi dowi finann Krstos doo shishiyo dek'at bísh azazetswotsi itwottsok'onat, bonat k'oshwotsnsh tewdi doo kitsosh b́ wottsotse jametswots Ik'o úditúne.  
\v 14 It atse fa'a s'eent kud'ts Ik'i s'aatatse tuutson itjangosh Ik'o k'onfetsr itn gawitune.  
\v 15 Ash noon keewon keewosh falerawo bí imtsosh Ik'o údeek wotowe. 
\c 10  
\s1 P'awlos b́finijangosh aani b́de'ktsok'o 
\p  
\v 1 Taa P'awlos it shinats twotor ááwu nefe eteyiri, itokere tworomó ááwu shúk'e eteyiri, Krstos doowootonat maac'nefon iti k'onirwe,  
\v 2 Meets ettsok'on no sha'irwok'o woshdek't taawiru ik ik ashuwots shinatse ááw shuuk'on keewo t geeyiyaloru itok twoor ááw shuk'on t keewitwok'o k'alk'ayere.  
\v 3 Dab datsanatse no beyaloru nokaarit datsatsi kaaraliye.  
\v 4 No kes' k'ac'onwere ááshet gop'o gaak faliyit Ik' ang detstswoni bako datsanatsi kes' k'ac'wotsiliye.  
\v 5 Ik'o danosh t'ug wotar tuwit mooshonat míshon gaaketwone, asaabi jamono k'aa'uder Krstossh bíaletwok'o woshitwone.  
\v 6 It aleyo s'een b́wotor konnari alek'azono sezosh k'andek'tswotsi wotitwone. 
\p  
\v 7 It its'iilirwo úratse bek'eyiru keewo s'uziye, asho konwor wotowa Krstosk taane ett bíatso amanirwo aanide'er t'iwintswe, noowere bíkok'o Krstosk nowottsok'o dande'e.  
\v 8 Doonzo noosh b́imts alon ayide'er ti it'alor bín jitseratse, alan noosh ime iti agosha bako gaakoshaliye.  
\v 9 T woshon itn t shatiyirwok'o ark'ye itsha.  
\v 10 Ik ikuwots «P'awlos woshwots mangtswotsnat kup'knee, bí b́tookon noonton b́wotormó maawke, b́ noon keew keewonwere k'awntsalke» etiirunee.  
\v 11 Man etiru ashuwots noo wokoon wotdek'at nowoshtswotsitse noguut'irwonat t karnonowere itnton wotdek'at nofiiniruwi dagotse k'osh k'osho b́beerawok'owo dande'ene. 
\p  
\v 12 B́ wotefere botoko údiru ash ik ikwotsnton no tooko nohiwosh wee notooko nuutsir s'iilosh ááwo shu'atsone, bomó botoko botookonton botatstsonat botookonowere botookonton bonohitsotse t'iwints dek'knaliye.  
\v 13 Noomó dab itok no borfetso Ik'o noosh b́ imts fini gúúron it'etuwoone bako tatsoniyere dambo id'atsone.  
\v 14 It beyruwere nofiiniru gúúrots b́wottsotse Krstos dooshishiyo daniyoh itok nowoor gúúrmaniyere besheratsone.  
\v 15 Mansha Ik'o noosh b́beezts gúúroniyere beshar k'oshwots finon weeralo id'atsone, maniyeremó it imnetiyo b́daboor Ik'o noosh b́beezts gúúrotse noon it mangitwok'o tewnirwone.  
\v 16 Eshe k'osh ashi fini gúúrots kindr shin fiinets finon noid'awo itiyere oke fa'a datswotsatse bíko doo shishi aap'o shishiyosh falfone. 
\p  
\v 17 \x - \xo 10:17 \xt Erm. 9:24\x* Ernmó «It'etwo doonzon id'ee.»  
\v 18 Asho údewosh b́bodet doonzo bín b́údora bako b́tooko b́tookon b́údoraliye. 
\c 11  
\s1 P'awlosnat kootets woshetswotsn 
\p  
\v 1 Taa muk'i dog t wottsotse taash it k'amitwok'o jangirwe, oona! taash k'amde'ere.  
\v 2 Baarna'a s'eenu ikukok'o iti kenih iko Krstossh twid'tsotse, Ik'i okooron okoorirwe.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 11:3 \xt Aze. 3:1-5\x* Dawunzo Hewaani weeri gondon b́ sheelitsok'o daneraka it asaabiyonwere awaashwtsar Krstossh itdetsts okooronat s'ayinon wottso it amanewo k'ayk'ritute etaat shatirwe.  
\v 4 Ik asho itok waar no nó nabtso b́woterawo k'osh Iyesusi itsh b́nabiyal wee it itdek'ts shayiro b́woteraniyere k'osh shayiro itdek'al, wee it dek'ts doo shishiyo b́ woterawo k'osh doo shishiyo it dek'al, s'k etaatni it dek'i etee. 
\p  
\v 5 Ernmó taa een een woshetswotsiyere jam keewon tdashtsok'o areratse.  
\v 6 Noon keewon dantso woto tk'azaloru dab dano taash shapatse, hanowere ayoto ay weeron kishdek' itsh danirone. 
\p  
\v 7 Taa Ik'i doo shushiyo itsh k'awntsalon tnabonat itn dambaan tizosh t tooko dashan t detso morrok'oweya b́ taaweyiri?  
\v 8 Itsh finosh k'osh Ik' moowwotsoke tep'o dek'at boon biik're.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 11:9 \xt Filp. 4:15-18\x* Itnton tbeyor taash wotit keewo b shapor, Mek'odoniyon waats t eshwots taash geyits jam keewon botep'irwotse konatsoru kuro woteratse, andish b́ borfetsosh itats jam keewon kuro woteratse, shino maantsisho kuro woteratse.  
\v 10 Krstos arikeewo t gitsotse b́ beyirwtse hanatse tuutson t id'awok'o woshitwo Akayiyi datsatse konworu aaliye.  
\v 11 B́ jango eebi? Itn shuno tk'ztsosheya? Itn tshuntsok'o Ik'o danfee. 
\p  
\v 12 K'osh wosheets manots, «No bonk'o finirwone» err boit'et weero t'ut'iyosh and tk'alirwok'o shino maantsoru dab k'alituwe.  
\v 13 Hank'o ashaanots Krstossh woshetswotsi aroosh botook wonawoniru kootets woshetswotsnat ash ant'elcef finetswotsiye.  
\v 14 Hanwere adiyit keewaliye, shed'anonworu dab shááno melakiwotsi aroosh b́ tooko b́woniti.  
\v 15 Mansh eshe shed'anosh finirwots kááwosh finirwotsi aroosh bo tooko bowoniyal noon adiratse, s'uwatse bo fini k'awntso daatsitune. 
\s1 P'awlos wosheetso b́wottsosh bíyats bodts kic'o 
\p  
\v 16 «Asho konwor dartso twottsok'o bísh ark'aye» err aani keewituwe. Dartsi twotiyaloru dab múk'i t it'etwok'o dartsok'o woshde'er taan taawwore.  
\v 17 Hank'o it'on tkeewor t keewirwo doonzo shunok'o b́ woterawo dartsok'o wotatniye.  
\v 18 Aywots meets keewon bo it'iruwosh taawor it'etuwe.  
\v 19 It t'iwintsirwotsi it wottsok'on dartswots jangosh gene'on k'amitute.  
\v 20 Hank'o konworu guutsok'o itn b́ woshiyal, konworu itko b́maal, iti b́finiyal, iti b́gac'iyal, it malalats b́ jabiyal k'amitute.  
\v 21 Taan jitsitka wotiyaloru dab keewanotsi finosh kup'uwotsi wotnok'azo itsh kitsitwe. 
\p Ernmó konwor it'osh ááwo b́ shúk'ol taaworu bíkok'o ááwo shúk'twe, hanowere ti etir and dartsok'o wotatniye.  
\v 22 Bo Ibrawi ashnowa? Taawere Ibrawi ash taane, bo Israe'el ashnowa? Taawere Israe'el ash taane, bo Abraham naarnowa? Taawere Abraham naar taane.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 11:23 \xt Wosh. 16:23\x* Bo Krstos guutsnowa? Taawere boyere bogo Krstossh guuts taane, hanowere ti etor geyetsok'o wotatniye t keewiri, boyere bogo ayoto finon mawure, ayoto tipere, ayoto jot'ere, ayoto k'iri t'up'er tawats bodre,  
\v 24 Útsoti shaashe jeed'iyoto ayhudiwots k'ac'eyon jot'ere,  
\v 25 \x - \xo 11:25 \xt Wosh. 16:22; 14:19\x* Keezoto gúmbon jot'ere, iknoto shútson k'is'ere, keezoto markabotse t'up'er tawo tiyats bodre, ik t'úwonat ik aawon aats k'aratse t teshi,  
\v 26 \x - \xo 11:26 \xt Wosh. 9:23; 14:15\x* T sha'i ayon foki s'eenonat aats di'on, biik'irwotsn bik'ewo ti'ats bodre, Ayhudi jirwotsnat Ik' ash woterawotsokere t'up'er tawo tiyats bodre, Kitonat worwotse aats k'aratsnowere t'up'er tawo tiyats bodre, mank'o kootets amantsuwotsoke t'up'ertawo tiyats bodre.  
\v 27 Ayo finonat maawo detsfe b́ teshi, ayoto tokro t t'utfoni, k'ak'efe, shashwefe, ayoto mish t'ut'o tiyats bodre, ak'onat araats woto tiyats bodre.  
\v 28 K'osh jam keewo t taawoniyere Ik'i moowwotsosh aawu aawon shiyanat t kic'efoni.  
\v 29 Maawrawo kone, taawor mááwratsta? ash iko morron b́ dihor taawer nib t k'únaw aawo egore? 
\p  
\v 30 It'o b́ geyitka wotink'e taa bín ti it'etwo taa maaw ash twoto kitsit keewwotsne,  
\v 31 Dúre dúrosh údeek wottso no doonz Iyesus nihi Ik'o t koorawok'o danfee.  
\v 32 Demask'o kitotse tbeyor nugúso Aretasiyere dashe dats k'eeziruwo taan detso geeyat kitutse bín keshet weero kotirwotsn b́ kotifere b́ teshi.  
\v 33 \x - \xo 11:33 \xt Wosh. 9:23-25\x* Wotowa bako ashuwots kas'i tungushi fúri weeron ooshon taan oorsh bok'rere b́ kishotse k'az t keshi. 
\c 12  
\s1 P'awlos bek'o 
\p  
\v 1 Dab it'otse daatset keewo b́ t'ut'aloru it'etwe, ernmo and doonzoke tdaatsts bek'onat be'etson keewo shunfee.  
\v 2 Krstosk wotts ik asho danfee, ashaan tatse awd natoniyere shinon keezl darok b́ borfetso b́ dek'eyi, b́ dek'ewewere b́ meetsontoni wotowa b́ meeston wot b́k'zo danatse, Ik'o danfee.  
\v 3 Ernmó ashaan Geneto maants b́ dek'etsok'o danfone, b́ meetson wotowá wotb́k'azon danatsone, Ik'o danfee,  
\v 4 Bíwere Geneto maants dek'eyat ash noon keewon keewosh falerawonat asho keewo b́ falaaw keewo b́ shishi.  
\v 5 Hank'o ashonn it'etuwe, t tokoshomó maawuk t wotoniyere okoon k'osh bín ti it'et keewo aaliye.  
\v 6 Eshe, taa ariko tkeewirwosh it'o tgeyiyalor dartsi woteratse, ernmó konwor tiatse b́bek'irwonat tiyoke b́k'ebirwoniyere bogshde'er taan b́s'iilawok'owa etaat it'atse tiatso kotdek'irwe. 
\p  
\v 7 Taash be'ets een een keewanotsatse tuutson t id'awok'o t meetso angitsok'o koshet weesho taash imeyi, hanuwere shed'ani melakiyo wotat taan túúzit onobek'shr ti id'awok'o taan b́woshiti.  
\v 8 Taan weeshiru keewan tiatse b́ k'aawu'etwok'o doonzo keezoto t k'oni.  
\v 9 Ernmó «Ti ango s'eenon b́fiinit n maaw manits b́wottsotse ts'aato neesh bodfe» taash bíeti, mansh Krstos ango tiats b́wotitwok'o jamoniyre bogo maawk twoton geneúfetsr it'o shunfee  
\v 10 Ango t daatsit maawk t wotor b́ wottsotse Krstos jangosh t maawor, t c'ashewor, gondo tbek'or, t gishewor, tkic'oro geneútwe. 
\p  
\v 11 Doogok'o keewre! eshe hank'o tkeewitwok'o taan k'altswots itne, taan údiyank'wots itna b́teshi, taa daneraw ash twotiyalor dab een eenne eteets woshetswotsiyere eegonor dasheraatse.  
\v 12 Ari wosheetso twoto kitsiru keewwots itnton tbewor k'amoon t k'alts fiinwotsiye, milikitanotsnat adits keewanotswere adiknee.  
\v 13 It ats kuro wot tk'azoniyere okoon k'osh Ik'i moowwotsiyere iti t dashiyi eegneya? Hanuwere naandok'o b́taawetka wotiyal taash oorowe erere! 
\p  
\v 14 Itok wosh k'andek' ttuwiyakon han keezloniye, taa itats kuro woto geeratse, taa tgeyir itna bako it gizoniyaliye. Bo nana'osh giz kakuwo b́s'ili ind nihwotsi bako nanaúwots indnihwotssh gizo ko'irakne.  
\v 15 Itsha err dab t gizonat t tookon beshide'er t imink'e ayideniye t geneuti, eshe taa itn ayidek'at t shunfere it taan it shunir hank'o múk'sh dek'atneya? 
\p  
\v 16 Ekewin wotowa hann wotowa taa itsh kuro woteratse, weeri gondonat ant'elcon iti tdetstsok'oye itsh bíari.?  
\v 17 T woshts ashuwotsitsere ikon dab kis'o keshrta?  
\v 18 Tito it maants b́ weetwok'o t k'oni, no eshu manowere bínton t woshi, eshe, Tito itoke t'k'miyo datsra? Taanat bín itsh nofin ik shayiron woteratsa? No sha sha'onwere ik woteratsa? 
\p  
\v 19 It únets andish b́ borfetsosh it gawir noo it shinatse notook jangosha etaat aninodek'irwok'o woshdek'aatni k'úna? Noo Krstosn wotdek'at nokeewirwo Ik'o shinaatsne, shuneetswotso! no jaman nokeewir iti kup'iyosha etaatniye.  
\v 20 Taa manmaants t woor daneraka it wotish t geyirwok'o it woterawon, taawere it itgeyirwok'o twoterawo gonketwonek'úna etaat shatirwe, mank'o itoke kaareyo, okooro, fayo, tookshuntsi woto, ash shúúts t'afiyo, óóno, bogtaana etonat dimbron beetúne etaat shatirwee.  
\v 21 Aani aanar itok twoor tiko Izar Izewer daneraka taan itshinatse ketitwe etaat shatirwe, haniyere shin bofints morratse tuutson kiimo, wido, shiraats jintsi wotatse tuutson naandrone eraaw ashuwots jangatse shiyanots kindiftak'úna etaat shatirwe. 
\c 13  
\s1 S'uwaatsi izonat jamon 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 13:1 \xt Iwi. 17:6; 19:15\x* Eshe, itok twoor han keezloniye taasha, awror b́wotiyal jam keewo arik b́ wotit wee git wee keez gawwotsne.  
\v 2 Gitlts s'iilo twoor itnton tteshor it tooko kor itdek'etwok'o keewatniye t teshi, andoor aaniy haniyere shin morro fintswotsnat k'oshwotsshor boatso korbodek'etwok'o keewitwe, and taa itok aanar twoor konshor maac'o k'eweratse,  
\v 3 It t gitsotse beyat keewirwo Krstosi b́wottsok'o dandek'oshe itgeyiri, itoke beyrwo b́kúp'a bako b́maawoniyaliye.  
\v 4 Bí mask'aliyats jiteyat b́k'ir maawona wotiyalor and Ik'i angon kashone b́ beyiri, noowere bíkok'o maawtswotsi woterone, itnton nodetsts gonkewok'onmó bínton Ik'i angon beetuwone. 
\p  
\v 5 It amantsatse it kúp'tsok'o sheengsh danosh it tooko t'iwintsde'er s'iilere, it atsono fads'iilere, Iyesus Krstos itgitsots b́wottsok'owo t'iwintsde'atsteya? Mank'o wotob́k'zal fadewor dihrte etee,  
\v 6 Noo fadewor nodihrawok'o dan itdek'etwok'owe nojangiri.  
\v 7 Gond keewo itk'alrawok'o Ik'o k'onirwone, Ik'o nok'onirwere no took faltswotsi wotat be'erani no'ooriyal it úni aawo sheeng wotts keewo it finitwok'owa bako tooko nofalo kitsoshaliye.  
\v 8 Noo ari keewosha nofinri bako ari keewo k'efitwo eegor k'alo falatsonee.  
\v 9 Noo maawtswotsi nowotere it kúp'uwotsi it wottsosh gene'úwirwone, no Ik'o nok'onir it s'eenwotsi it wotitwok'owe.  
\v 10 Woshan itoke wokdek' befetsat tguut'ir manatse tuutsone, hank'on itok twoor doonzo taash b́ imts alon itn kic'iratse, doonzo alo taash b́ im itn tiagisha bako iti gaakoshaliye. 
\p  
\v 11 Eshe ti eshúwotso! jamon beewere! it bebeyo manutside'ere, t izonowere beewere, it ats atseyosh ikwotore, jeenon beewere, shunonat jeeniko Izar Izewer itnton wotituwe. 
\p  
\v 12 S'ayin wotts jobon jobeyar jamo aatewere. 
\p  
\v 13 Amants jamwots jamo itsh t'intsirune. 
\p  
\v 14 Doonzo Iyesus Krstos s'aato, Ik' shuno, S'ayin shayro ik woto it únetsnton wotowe.